Packages
game In this package we save the representation of a general sigma-game and have the mathematical methods to calculate solutions and core elements.
gui In this package the abstract graphical user interface is saved.
guigraph In this package the graphical user interface for the sigma game on graphs.
guitrisentis Here we find the graphical user interface for the Trisentis game and sigma game on grids.
help Some classes which have nothing to do with the project itself, but are needed for implementing or showing nice results in the command line.
test Some classes which test the sigma game on different graphs.
test.tree Tests the sigma game on trees.
trisentis Implements the sigma game as Trisentis game with some special features which are only useful to analyse the Trisentis game.
